      "description": "Available now is an exceptional 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, a definitive icon of JDM performance. This specimen features the legendary 2JZ-GTE 3.0L twin-turbocharged inline-six engine, delivering linear power through its factory-original sequential induction system. Power is managed by the coveted Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox and delivered to the rear wheels via a Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis maintains its original structural integrity, complemented by a four-wheel independent double-wishbone suspension that remains tight and precise. Retaining its factory-spec intercooler, oil cooler, and ventilated disc brakes with four-piston calipers, this A80 represents a rare opportunity to own an unmodified, mechanically pristine legend. The exterior finish exhibits excellent luster with matching VIN tags across all panels, and the interior remains free of bolster wear or UV degradation.",
